{
  "_comment": "Curated list — only sources tested as working as of 2026-06. Failing RSS feeds (Impactpool, UNTalent, Devex) were removed because they now return HTML/empty rather than feeds, or are protected by Cloudflare. ReliefWeb is the most productive source (200+ jobs per scan). LinkedIn is best-effort and frequently blocked. HTML scrapes on big-org career sites (AfDB, EBRD, World Bank) work but yield few items due to JS rendering — they're kept as low-yield-but-zero-cost signal sources.",
